data.description: Presenting a charming new listing located at 1730 Price Drive, Farmville, VA. This lovely property features three bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, and a host of modern upgrades, including stylish Zodiac solid surface countertops and sleek stainless steel appliances. This home has a two-car garage, a partially finished basement with a full bathroom, and gym equipment that conveys with the sale of the home. Step out onto the spacious rear deck and take in the peaceful vista of the private backyard. Don't miss the chance to call this beautifully enhanced house your new home.
